# Frontend — Next.js Rules

- Use App Router conventions when applicable
- Keep page components thin; delegate to feature components
- Use server components by default; client only when needed
- Colocate data fetching with the component that uses it or in dedicated loaders
- Use consistent file naming: kebab-case for files, PascalCase for components

Avoid large page files; split into sections and components.
